      "questionNumber": 8,
      "questionText": "If $$x$$ is positive, the first negative term in the expansion of $${\\left( {1 + x} \\right)^{27/5}}$$ is ",
      "options": [
        "6th term ",
        "7th term ",
        "5th term ",
